title: Schedule A Tour-Newly Renovated Apartment Homes And Luxury Amenities!
posting_body: ['The Durham features just the right blend of charm and the ideal location for your next home.', 'Our community offers a variety of spacious apartment homes ranging from one-bedroom to three-bedroom floor plans.', 'Residents enjoy breathtaking views from our balconies, generous closet space, quartz counters, plank flooring and much, much more!', 'The Durham is nestled in the suburb of Edina with easy access to several major highways.', '-The Cyber Lounge Hosts a 24-hr, Self-Serve Coffee Bar, Pool Table and Computer Stations Making This a Great Place to Connect and Recharge', '-High Intensity UVC Lamp Coupled with Bionic iWave Air Purifying Systems', '-Moen Align bathroom collection in a chrome finish for a modern look', '-Engineered wood plank flooring throughout', '-Large, private balcony with panoramic views', '-Well Equipped Tech Center with Mac and PC Computers and Multi-Function Printer', '-Package Concierge Offering 24-Hour Access to Packages', '-Extra stuff?', 'Convenient Storage Lockers Available', '-Dedicated Laundry Facilities with High Efficiency Equipment and Onsite Dry Cleaning', '-The Event Features a Demonstration Kitchen with Enough Room to Entertain a Few Close Friends or a Crowd', '-Certified 100% sprinklered apartments', '-The Cinema Offers Cozy Seating for Private Viewing Parties', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>']
